{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab 5.1 output router\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab output switcher (1 of 8 channels)\sa180\par}
